definitions.definition: A young offspring of a various carnivores ( canid , ursid , felid , pinniped ), especially of a dog or a wolf , the young of a bear or similar mammal ( lion , tiger , seal ); a pup , wolf cub .
An insolent youth ; a mere child .
One of several wooden strips to prevent wear on a windlass on a clipper-era ship.
A tooth on a sprocket wheel (compare sprocket and cog ).
